{
  "stem": "8359.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't even judge it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wasn't too far, maybe 20 minutes or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when we were transferred there, we were now in a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a hell of a difference.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Haase.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huge.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Much bigger than ours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few levels of living quarters, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, women.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so help me, good God, they're worse than men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "SS women in uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they walked us to and from work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would search us to make sure-- that's why I said I don't know how I got away with that smuggling that thing for my period.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would search us, if they had any suspicion, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the war wasn't going, so Hitler was in already fighting to France, you know, United States and Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was cut off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No more, no more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1943, in the middle of 1943.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that this was a punishment for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- do you remember Heydrich-- Henry-- Heinrich-- Heydrich?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a big, big-- Hitler's--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--deputy or something?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was assassinated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he's the one that wiped out Lidice, that-- the city in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think this was our punishment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was our punishment, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when all hell broke loose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when-- that's when we hurt really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The funny thing-- this-- I swear, I don't know how people's mind-- she was better to her own girls than she was to us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because while-- because she had the type of camp that we had in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She got a group of girls that came in maybe three or four months later than we did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a hell of a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but she-- she was inclined because she knew them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
